item.title: Easter Service Times
item.description: Easter Service Times 14th April The Maundy Thursday meal & service will be at St Alban’s commencing at 6pm 15th April Good Friday service will be a one Parish service, at St Alban’s commencing at 8am 16th April Easter Eve Vigil service will be at St Augustine’s commencing at 6.30pm 17th April Easter Day service will also be a one Parish Service, at St Alban’s commencing at 9am.
